{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The library has been completely updated for Swift 6 language mode, and now compiles in strict"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"concurrency with no warnings or errors."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigrationGuides"]]},"metadata":{"role":"article","roleHeading":"Article","title":"Migrating to 1.15","modules":[{"name":"ComposableArchitecture"}]},"kind":"article","seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.19","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.18","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17.1","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.16","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.14","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.13","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.12","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.11","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.10","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.9","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.8","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.7","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.6","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.5","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.4"]}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/composablearchitecture\/migratingto1.15"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The library is now 100% Swift 6 compatible, and has been done in a way that is full backwards","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"compatible. If your project does not have strict concurrency warnings turned on, then updating","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the Composable Architecture to 1.15.0 should not cause any compilation errors. However, if you have","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"strict concurrency turned on, then you may come across a few situations you need to update.","type":"text"}]},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Enum cases as function references","anchor":"Enum-cases-as-function-references"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"It is common to use the case of enum as a function, such as mapping on an ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Effect","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" to bundle","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"its output into an action:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["return client.fetch()","  .map(Action.response)"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In strict concurrency mode this may fail with a message like this:"}]},{"name":"Note","type":"aside","style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"🛑 Converting non-sendable function value to ‘@Sendable (Value) -> Action’ may introduce data races"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"There are two ways to fix this. You can either open the closure explicitly instead of using"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"Action.response","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" as a function:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["return client.fetch()","  .map { .response($0) }"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"There is also an upcoming Swift feature that will fix this. You can enable it in an SPM package","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"by adding a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"enableUpcomingFeature"},{"text":" to its Swift settings:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["swiftSettings: [","  .enableUpcomingFeature(\"InferSendableFromCaptures\"),","]),"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"And you can "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/www.swift.org\/blog\/using-upcoming-feature-flags\/","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by navigating to your project’s build settings in Xcode, and adding a new “Other Swift Flags” flag:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":null,"code":["-enable-upcoming-feature InferSendableFromCaptures"],"type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.15","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"references":{"doc://ComposableArchitecture/documentation/ComposableArchitecture/Store":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"Store"}],"abstract":[{"text":"A store represents the runtime that powers the application. It is the object that you will pass","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"around to views that need to interact with the application.","type":"text"}],"title":"Store","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Store","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"Store"}],"url":"\/documentation\/composablearchitecture\/store","kind":"symbo